Based on your observations, the 'Control Relay' was found to be closed during inspection. Since the step required observing the relay both while powered on and off to check its state in both conditions, but only a single observation ("is_closed: True") was reported—with no mention of a power state change—there is incomplete evidence to fully assess normal relay function.

However, if this observation was made when the relay should be powered off, then the relay being closed may suggest the problem 'ReleStuckClosed' (the relay contact is stuck closed). If powered on, closed is expected in most designs. 

